from\": 626, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"atrocity crimes\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the letters, CSI's international president, Dr. John Eibner, pointed out that the president of Azerbaijan's National Olympic Committee, Ilham Aliyev, is also the \\\"dictatorial president of the Republic of Azerbaijan itself,\\\" who \\\"ordered a military invasion\\\" of Nagorno Karabakh \\\"after imposing a devastating nine-month blockade of its Armenian Christian population.\\\"\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Committee_for_Skeptical_Inquiry\", \"score\": 0.922868076377078, \"rank\": 0.05241916265353041, \"text\": \"CSI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Committee_for_Skeptical_Inquiry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Committee_for_Skeptical_Inquiry\"}, {\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Eibner\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\"}, {\"begin\": 764, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"score\": 0.9999993030676405, \"rank\": 6.220295993371169e-07, \"text\": \"Azerbaijan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9998856922900775, \"rank\": 0.00011432070705307535, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re