 \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eibner noted that it was with the support of the G7 that, two years ago, the IOC decided to exclude the Russian and Belarussian national teams from the 2024 Olympics, after Russia invaded Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_of_Seven\", \"score\": 0.9995759570200728, \"rank\": 0.00042422286860505906, \"text\": \"G7\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_of_Seven\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_of_Seven\"}, {\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.835291786265584e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9967319539340981, \"rank\": 0.0020616063154719603, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russia invaded Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russia invaded Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Russian_invasion_of_Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eibner\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ilham Aliyev's Azerbaijan is no less deserving of such punitive measures,\\\" Eibner said.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilham_Aliyev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ilham Aliyev\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilham_Aliyev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilham_Aliyev\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"score\": 0.9999993030676405, \"rank\": 6.220295993371169e-07, \"text\": \"Azerbaijan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such punitive measures\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"Eibner\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To do otherwise sends powerful messages to Olympian dictators, like Ilham Aliyev, that they can commit atrocity crimes with impunity unless the G7 consortium finds them unacceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999914949101073, \"rank\": 7.986721019496073e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilham_Aliyev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ilham Aliyev\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"w